channel.title: Okay, I was using Moparscape Cm alexia's tutorial on how to set class paths
channel.description:
I was setting the variable for Classpath and got stuck... I was about to put this in
[code]CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin;%CLASSPATH%;.[/code]
But then I wasn't sure if I was supposed to put something where it says ;%CLASSPATH%; or take it out, or just leave it exactly like that.
Anyone know?
